In [23]:
for file in ("SMALL_.csv", "BIG_.csv"):
    data = pd.read_csv("../data/" + file)
    for typ in ("small_vals", "big_vals", "almost_sorted", "reversed"):
        plt.plot(data["array size"].values, data[[h for h in data.columns if typ in h]].values)
        plt.xlabel("size")
        plt.ylabel("time, ms")
        plt.title(typ)
        plt.legend([h[:h.find('_')] for h in data.columns if typ in h])
        plt.show()

In [48]:
for file in ("SMALL_.csv", "BIG_.csv"):
    data = pd.read_csv("../data/" + file)
    for typ in ("SelectionSort", "BubbleSort",    "BubbleSortA1", "BubbleSortA1&2",
                             "InsertionSort", "InserionSortB", "CountingSort", "LSD",
                             "MergeSort",     "QuickSortH",    "QuickSortL",   "HeapSort"):
        plt.plot(data["array size"].values, data[[h for h in data.columns if h[:h.find('_')] == typ]].values)
        plt.xlabel("size")
        plt.ylabel("time, ms")
        plt.title(typ)
        plt.legend([h[h.find('_')+1:] for h in data.columns if typ in h])
        plt.show()

for file in ("SMALL_.csv", "BIG_.csv"):
    data = pd.read_csv("../data/" + file)
    for typ in ("small_vals", "big_vals", "almost_sorted", "reversed"):
        plt.plot(data["array size"].values, data[[h for h in data.columns if typ in h 
                                                 and "Bubble" not in h and "Insertion" not in h
                                                 and "Selection" not in h
                                                 and "Inserion" not in h]].values)
        plt.xlabel("size")
        plt.ylabel("time, ms")
        plt.title(typ)
        plt.legend([h[:h.find('_')] for h in data.columns if typ in h
                   and "Bubble" not in h and "Insertion" not in h
                                                 and "Selection" not in h
                   and "Inserion" not in h])
        plt.show()
